data.description: Seller has a VA assumable loan at 2.55%. Call for more info! Welcome to this stunning 1.5-story home with 5 bedrooms, 4.5 baths, and a 3-car garage. The main floor impresses with a 2-story entry, great room, and a gourmet kitchen featuring a center island and walk-in pantry. There's an adjacent office space for your convenience. The main floor also houses a spacious master suite with a spa-like bathroom and a large walk-in closet. Upstairs, three additional bedrooms have direct bathroom access. And don't miss the recently finished basement, complete with a full wet bar for your entertainment needs. This home blends elegance, functionality, and entertainment seamlessly.
